nodes.text: A battle occurred on a planet sometime during the Clone Wars. It occurred when the clone armies of the Galactic Republic stormed the planet, controlled by the Confederacy of Independent Systems, in order to raid its banks of Separatist treasure. During the battle, Wes Apice destroyed a droid cannon attacking clone troopers, although not before the clones were wiped out. However, after the cannon's destruction, a clone trooper commander finished up the fighting, and cleaned out the last bank.
